  {
    "hotel_id": "297770",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/apa-hotel-namba-shinsaibashi/hotel/osaka-jp.html",
    "name": "APA Hotel Namba-Shinsaibashi",
    "detail": "First off, I appreciated booking through Agoda.com. They provided great customer service and pricing. My room was as small as a postage stamp for a hotel in Osaka. But really I had no issue with it, as I’m a solo traveler. The Wi-Fi in the room was perfect and super-fast. The room was minimally decorated, clean and in good repair. I was left a bottle of water everyday by the cleaning staff. It was a nice option to have in my purse when I was running out the door. There was a kettle and a small fridge in the room. It was also nice to have if you didn’t want to run out and get a breakfast in the a.m.’s. The Bathroom was always well stocked. The location of the hotel is very convenient to Osaka-Namba station. There were some cheap and cheerful places close to the hotel to grab food. The street the hotel was on was pretty quiet and I never experienced any issues when I left early in the a.m. and came home in the early evening. ",
